    "description": "<strong>本次Demo<br>主要开放了两组回响之地，分别是“雪域之地”以及“水晶矿洞”。<br>总共可以收集的回响之牌为18张。<br>冒险者可以解锁以及挑战的最高回响深度（难度）为III阶。<br>最高装备阶级开放5阶（普通-白，精良-绿，稀有-蓝，史诗-金，传说-橙色）。<br>最高人物等级上限为25级。<br>最多可以获取两种召唤圣物。</strong><br><br><strong>冒险者们欢迎加入我们的玩家社群和QQ官方群，请告诉我们对这款游戏的想法和意见。<br>每一位玩家的建议、思路、以及愤怒，我们都会认真对待，它们都拥有极高的价值，是我们迭代更新的重要依据和参考<br>《七度荒域》玩家Q群：572433049</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/ac6ae064dcbc78d251af6e509c1fee11.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.poster.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.webm?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/971d6e6d51dfbfe27f4f5b71126a6b9f.mp4?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>ACT之名打造极致2D像素类战斗体验!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/2f666634c73842e82d033d42a81094f6.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.poster.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.webm?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/ff72bc24742d918eb7c4dbd83ad4a9ec.mp4?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>这世界提供多样化武器与技能的搭配，每种搭配都可以带来不同的策略和战斗体验。<br>同时也结合了横版动作游戏的特性，来为这世界创造秘密。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/54f38815ef8c1f02f288480a19c62a38.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.poster.avif?t=1755072974\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.webm?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/bdebc306124775ec701ec2e3ae7ccee9.mp4?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Rogue类刷宝收集是猎人的最爱<br>这世界提供繁多的装备词缀，可以组装成各种不同的属性战术方式。<br>用这样的机制取代来致敬剑与魔法时代的追求。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/930c77017c4f63d891870d7fde2144df.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.poster.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.webm?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/98e9c28a9e6aad9a4f4901a35ce87b4f.mp4?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>这个世界拥有等级，也拥有重复死亡，这样的前进方式，需要你我的追寻。<br>在致敬也是在前进。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/7d7bc7d525293124398d1519901dcc8c.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=108 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.poster.avif?t=1755072974\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.webm?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137200/extras/0231464ea20fcd1ae679dd69b8646471.mp4?t=1755072974\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>可以组装成不同的属性和战术方法。取而代之的是<br>传统天赋装备粘贴构建与搭配、有趣的事件线索<br>与神秘的回声卡牌、3D像素变换技术于一体</strong>",
